Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:22:00.95,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}刚刚 你欲言又止的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:07.52,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}悄然落在我指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:13.11,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}你什么都不用说
