Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.60,0:23:56.57,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我想守护重要的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.89,0:24:02.55,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}无论何时 两人都不孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:09.86,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}哪怕会破坏我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:15.65,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也希望你来触摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.17,0:24:26.43,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}痛苦异常 心急难耐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.54,0:24:32.34,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}无法回头 想就这样走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.50,0:24:39.55,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因为指尖感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.75,0:24:46.10,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你的真心话语
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:50.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}じゃあまたね 手を振った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:56.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}うしろ姿 あんなに もう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:03.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}夕暮れの人波に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:08.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}揺れながら 小さくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:15.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}あなたがくれた 言葉を
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}ひとつづつ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:24.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}思い出し 目を閉じた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:30.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}幸せな思いだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:37.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}ここにあるはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:44.97,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}不安になる どうしてなの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:50.48,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}心がふるえてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:56.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}伝えたいもっと そう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:02.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}あふれてる この気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:10.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}好きだから 好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:15.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}ぜったい好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:26.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}振り向いて かけ出して
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:31.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}追いかけていきたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:38.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}夕暮れの 寂しさが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:43.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}そんな勇気飲み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:50.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}あなたの笑顔の中に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:53.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}わたしはいる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:59.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}すこし離れただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:05.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}迷子になったような
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:12.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}こどもみたい 泣きだしそう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:19.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}素直なら こんな思い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:25.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}しなくてもすむのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:31.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}からっぽのわたしだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:38.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}ここにいて 叫んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:45.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}好きだから 好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:51.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}ぜったい好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:50.95,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}那么再见了 我挥了挥手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:56.13,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}你的背影 已经如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:03.84,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}在傍晚的人潮中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:08.70,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}一边摇晃一边远去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:15.28,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}你对我说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.33,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}每一句话语
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:24.53,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}回想起来 我闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:30.82,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}应该只有幸福的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:37.56,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:44.97,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}却会变得不安 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:50.48,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}心在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:56.09,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}我想再多告诉你一些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:02.62,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}充满心怀的这份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:10.33,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}因为喜欢你 因为喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:15.91,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}因为我绝对喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:26.17,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}转过身来 向你奔去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:31.72,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}虽然我想去追赶你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:38.62,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}傍晚的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:43.74,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}将这份勇气吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:50.04,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}在你的笑容中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:53.75,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}有我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:59.89,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}只是离开一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:05.89,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}你就像迷了路一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:12.71,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}仿佛孩子一样 就要哭起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:19.70,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}如果坦率的话 这种痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:25.62,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}就不必经历了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:31.21,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}只有空无一物的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:38.26,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}在这里呼唤着你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:45.41,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}因为喜欢你 因为喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:51.80,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}因为我绝对喜欢你